metadata.name: #01 - Kin
metadata.description:
Name: Kin
Blood group: B
Gender: Male
Date of birth: September 13th
Story:
Kin is a half-breed child whose father is Japanese and mother is English. He was raised with strict and proper manners since he was a child, but this led to his strong desire to break free and runaway when he grows up. He eventually became a Tsuppari.
His closest friend, Momo, is the one who made him change and turn back to the right track. 
They got married and have 1 boy and 1 girl.
Favorite motto: " Let's go "
